/*:
 ### Final Page
 When should you start to invest? The short answer is as soon as possible . If you start earlier, the amount of contribution you need to make each month will be smaller and it will be easier for you. You will also feel the benefit of compound interest if you start earlier. Run the code to see the visualization.
 */

/*:
 As you can see you need to make bigger contribution represented by taller box each month if you start later. But by starting earlier you can make a smaller contribution represented by a shorter box.
 I hope after you finish this playground , you will understand about this matter more and make the best choice for your life. Thank you for sticking with this playground until the last page.
 */

